<div class="container-white">    
    <div class="page-header">
        <h1>How to order?</h1>
    </div>


    <div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne">1. You want to order with Top Menu? It's easy.
                    <i class="ion-arrow-down-b pull-right" data-pack="default" data-tags="" style="display: inline-block;"></i>
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    Enter your <span class="text-red">postal code</span> on the home page. The first 3 characters are enough then click on "GO !" and you will find the list for all the restaurants that delivers to you.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTen">2. Feeling peckish for something special? No problems
                    <i class="ion-arrow-down-b pull-right" data-pack="default" data-tags="" style="display: inline-block;"></i>
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseTen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    You can choose the <span class="text-red">cuisine type</span> that makes you happy by selecting it from the list on your left.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEleven">3. You found a restaurant?
                    <i class="ion-arrow-down-b pull-right" data-pack="default" data-tags="" style="display: inline-block;"></i>
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseEleven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <ul>
						<li>
		                    That delivers in <strong class="text-red">Plateau, Villeray, Centre-Sud, Rosemont, Hochelaga, Outremont or Centre-Ville Est.</strong>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<p>
		                Choose the dishes you like. When you choose a dish a pop up appears so you can choose the quantity and any options available for this dish. By clicking "ok" your selection is added to your basket.				
					</p>
					<ul>
						<li>
		                    For all the other sectors you can read the PDF menu of the restaurant and then communicate directly with the restaurant.
						</li>
					</ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwelve">4. Ready to order? Let's do it!	
                    <i class="ion-arrow-down-b pull-right" data-pack="default" data-tags="" style="display: inline-block;"></i>
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseTwelve" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>
                		Once your order finish you will need to:
					</p>
					<ol>
		                <li>
		                    Connect or create your Top Menu account
						</li>
						<li>
		                    Confirm your order
						</li>
						<li>
		                    To choose between delivery and pick-up
						</li>
		                <li>
		                    Enter your credit card information or choose to pay at the door
		                </li>
		                <li>
		                    Click proceed to payment
		                </li>
					</ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThirteen">5. What happens when you order is sent?
                    <i class="ion-arrow-down-b pull-right" data-pack="default" data-tags="" style="display: inline-block;"></i>
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseThirteen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <p>
		                Once the order done, it's sent to the restaurant which will shortly respond to you, on the web page, the expected delivery time.
					</p>
					<p>
						If for some reason the restaurants declines the order your payment will not go through.
					</p>
					<p>
		                You will receive an email to confirm your order
					</p>
		            <br/>
					<p>
		                Don't forget to tip the driver.
					</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>